450744,106,2573,2,4,1,22,2,7 . Guttātherīgāthāvaṇṇanā 
450745,106,2574,2,9,1,53,6,Gutte yadatthaṃ {pabbajjā}tiādikā guttāya theriyā gāthā. 
450746,106,2574,10,36,1,254,24,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikārā tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinantī anukkamena sambhatavimokkhasambhārā hutvā, paripakkakusalamūlā sugatīsuyeva saṃsarantī imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattā, guttā tissā nāmaṃ ahosi. "
450747,106,2574,37,49,1,133,12,Sā viññutaṃ patvā upanissayasampattiyā codiyamānā gharāvāsaṃ jigucchantī mātāpitaro anujānāpetvā mahāpajāpatigotamiyā santike pabbaji. 
450748,106,2574,50,65,1,132,13,"Pabbajitvā ca vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā bhāvanaṃ anuyuñjantiyā tassā cittaṃ cirakālaparicayena bahiddhārammaṇe vidhāvati, ekaggaṃ nāhosi. "
450749,106,2574,66,83,1,134,16,"Satthā disvā taṃ anuggaṇhanto, gandhakuṭiyaṃ yathānisinnova obhāsaṃ pharitvā tassā āsanne ākāse nisinnaṃ viya attānaṃ dassetvā ovadanto– "
