450768,106,2592,12,16,1,16,3,– imā gāthā ābhāsi; 
450769,106,2593,2,12,1,96,9,Tattha tameva {anubrūhehī}ti yadatthaṃ yassa kilesaparinibbānassa khandhaparinibbānassa ca atthāya. 
450770,106,2593,13,31,1,156,17,"Hitvā puttaṃ vasuṃ piyan ti piyāyitabbaṃ ñātiparivaṭṭaṃ bhogakkhandhañca hitvā mama sāsane pabbajjā brahmacariyavāso icchito, tameva vaḍḍheyyāsi sampādeyyāsi. "
450771,106,2593,32,44,1,98,11,Mā cittassa vasaṃ {gamī}ti dīgharattaṃ rūpādiārammaṇavasena vaḍḍhitassa kūṭacittassa vasaṃ mā gacchi. 
450772,106,2594,2,13,1,94,10,"Yasmā cittaṃ nāmetaṃ māyūpamaṃ, yena vañcitā andhaputhujjanā māravasānugā saṃsāraṃ nātivattanti. "
450773,106,2594,14,23,1,34,5,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ cittena vañcitā’’ tiādi. 
450774,106,2595,2,18,1,104,10,Saṃyojanāni {etānī}ti etāni‘‘ kāmacchandañca byāpādan’’ tiādinā yathāvuttāni pañca bandhanaṭṭhena saṃyojanāni. 
450775,106,2595,19,23,1,43,3,{Pajahitvānā}ti anāgāmimaggena samucchinditvā. 
450776,106,2595,24,28,1,26,3,{Bhikkhunī}ti tassā ālapanaṃ. 
450777,106,2595,29,40,1,127,10,{Orambhāgamanīyānī}ti rūpārūpadhātuto heṭṭhābhāge kāmadhātuyaṃ manussajīvassa hitāni upakārāni tattha paṭisandhiyā paccayabhāvato. 
450778,106,2595,41,43,1,21,2,Ma-kāro padasandhikaro.
450779,106,2595,44,54,1,34,5,"‘‘ Oramāgamanīyānī’’ ti pāḷi, so evattho. "
450780,106,2595,55,68,1,119,11,Nayidaṃ {punarehisī}ti orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ pahānena idaṃ kāmaṭṭhānaṃ kāmabhavaṃ paṭisandhivasena puna nāgamissasi. 
450781,106,2595,69,71,1,21,2,Ra-kāro padasandhikaro.
450782,106,2595,72,84,1,50,7,"‘‘ Itthan’’ ti vā pāḷi, itthattaṃ kāmabhavamicceva attho. "
