451240,106,2856,2,24,1,93,8,"‘ ‘ Sakalamevidaṃ, ānanda, brahmacariyaṃ yadidaṃ kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā’’( saṃ. ni.5.2)."
451241,106,2856,25,51,1,171,15,"‘‘ Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, meghiya, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ kalyāṇasahāyassa kalyāṇasampavaṅkassa yaṃ sīlavā bhavissati pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvuto viharissatī’’ ti( udā.31) ca evamādinā pasaṃsitā. "
