451448,106,2956,37,46,1,96,9,Tesaṃ pana sabbesampi karaṇḍakesu nipajjāpitadivasesuyeva puññiddhiyā aṅguṭṭhato khīraṃ nibbatti. 
451449,106,2956,47,55,1,80,8,Sakko devarājā tassa rañño nikkaṅkhabhāvatthaṃ antokaraṇḍake akkharāni likhāpesi–
