454264,107,79,27,60,1,252,29,"Yathā ca naranāriyo ukkārabhūmiyaṃ uccārapassāvaṃ katvā na taṃ ucchaṅgena vā ādāya, dussantena vā veṭhetvā gacchanti, jigucchamānā pana anapekkhāva, chaḍḍetvā gacchanti, evaṃ mayāpi imaṃ pūtikāyaṃ anapekkhena chaḍḍetvā amatanibbānanagaraṃ pavisituṃ vaṭṭati. "
