454329,107,117,2,22,1,196,20,Abhiññābalamāharin ti pacchā tasmiṃ assame vasanto kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā abhiññānañca samāpattīnañca uppādanatthāya aniccato ca dukkhato ca vipassanaṃ ārabhitvā thāmappattaṃ vipassanābalaṃ āhariṃ. 
