454368,107,130,2,3,1,16,2,Dīpaṅkaro buddho 
454369,107,131,2,14,1,101,11,Evaṃ abhiññābalaṃ patvā sumedhatāpase samāpattisukhena vītināmente dīpaṅkaro nāma satthā loke udapādi. 
454370,107,131,15,31,1,164,13,"Tassa paṭisandhijātibodhi dhammacakkappavattanesu sakalāpi dasasahassilokadhātu saṅkampi sampakampi sampavedhi, mahāviravaṃ ravi, dvattiṃsa pubbanimittāni pāturahesuṃ. "
