454436,107,178,2,15,1,114,12,So pana kalalapiṭṭhe nipannakova puna akkhīni ummīletvā dīpaṅkaradasabalassa buddhasiriṃ sampassamāno evaṃ cintesi–
454437,107,178,16,57,1,314,33,"‘‘ sace ahaṃ iccheyyaṃ, sabbakilese jhāpetvā saṅghanavako hutvā rammanagaraṃ paviseyyaṃ, aññātakavesena pana me kilese jhāpetvā nibbānappattiyā kiccaṃ natthi, yaṃnūnāhaṃ dīpaṅkaradasabalo viya paramābhisambodhiṃ patvā dhammanāvaṃ āropetvā mahājanaṃ saṃsārasāgarā uttāretvā pacchā parinibbāyeyyaṃ, idaṃ mayhaṃ patirūpan’’ ti. "
454438,107,178,58,66,1,70,8,Tato aṭṭha dhamme samodhānetvā buddhabhāvāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipajji. 
454439,107,178,67,69,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
454440,107,179,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Pathaviyaṃ nipannassa, evaṃ me āsi cetaso;"
454441,107,180,2,10,1,39,7,"‘ Icchamāno ahaṃ ajja, kilese jhāpaye mama."
454442,107,181,2,13,1,43,6,"‘ ‘‘ Kiṃ me aññātavesena, dhammaṃ sacchikatenidha; "
454443,107,182,2,8,1,44,5,"Sabbaññutaṃ pāpuṇitvā, buddho hessaṃ sadevake."
454444,107,183,2,12,1,42,7,"‘ ‘‘ Kiṃ me ekena tiṇṇena, purisena thāmadassinā; "
454445,107,184,2,7,1,43,4,"Sabbaññutaṃ pāpuṇitvā, santāressaṃ sadevakaṃ."
454446,107,185,2,11,1,38,6,"‘ ‘‘ Iminā me adhikārena, katena purisuttame; "
454447,107,186,2,8,1,42,5,"Sabbaññutaṃ pāpuṇitvā, tāremi janataṃ bahuṃ."
454448,107,187,2,11,1,46,6,"‘ ‘‘ Saṃsārasotaṃ chinditvā, viddhaṃsetvā tayo bhave; "
454449,107,188,2,11,1,46,5,"Dhammanāvaṃ samāruyha, santāressaṃ sadevakan’’’ ti. "
454450,107,189,2,6,1,34,4,Yasmā pana buddhattaṃ patthentassa–
454451,107,190,2,9,1,47,5,"‘ ‘ Manussattaṃ liṅgasampatti, hetu satthāradassanaṃ; "
454452,107,191,2,8,1,42,5,"Pabbajjā guṇasampatti, adhikāro ca chandatā; "
454453,107,192,2,9,1,45,4,"Aṭṭhadhammasamodhānā , abhinīhāro samijjhatī’’ ti. "
454454,107,193,2,21,1,149,18,"Manussattabhāvasmiṃyeva hi ṭhatvā buddhattaṃ patthentassa patthanā samijjhati, nāgassa vā supaṇṇassa vā devatāya vā sakkassa vā patthanā no samijjhati. "
454455,107,193,22,34,1,124,11,"Manussattabhāvepi purisaliṅge ṭhitasseva patthanā samijjhati, itthiyā vā paṇḍakanapuṃsakaubhatobyañjanakānaṃ vā no samijjhati. "
454456,107,193,35,45,1,95,9,"Purisassapi tasmiṃ attabhāve arahattappattiyā hetusampannasseva patthanā samijjhati, no itarassa. "
454457,107,193,46,62,1,156,15,"Hetusampannassāpi jīvamānabuddhasseva santike patthentasseva patthanā samijjhati, parinibbute buddhe cetiyasantike vā bodhimūle vā patthentassa na samijjhati. "
454458,107,193,63,73,1,90,9,"Buddhānaṃ santike patthentassapi pabbajjāliṅge ṭhitasseva samijjhati, no gihiliṅge ṭhitassa. "
454459,107,193,74,83,1,98,7,"Pabbajitassapi pañcābhiññāaṭṭhasamāpattilābhinoyeva samijjhati, na imāya guṇasampattiyā virahitassa. "
454460,107,193,84,100,1,131,14,"Guṇasampannenapi yena attano jīvitaṃ buddhānaṃ pariccattaṃ hoti, tasseva iminā adhikārena adhikārasampannassa samijjhati, na itarassa. "
454461,107,193,101,120,1,140,17,"Adhikārasampannassāpi yassa buddhakārakadhammānaṃ atthāya mahanto chando ca ussāho ca vāyāmo ca pariyeṭṭhi ca, tasseva samijjhati, na itarassa. "
454462,107,194,2,24,1,164,18,"Tatridaṃ chandamahantatāya opammaṃ– sace hi evamassa yo sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ ekodakībhūtaṃ attano bāhubalena uttaritvā pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
454463,107,194,25,41,1,134,15,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ veḷugumbasañchannaṃ viyūhitvā madditvā padasā gacchanto pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
454464,107,194,42,59,1,145,16,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ sattiyo ākoṭetvā nirantaraṃ sattiphalasamākiṇṇaṃ padasā akkamamāno pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇāti. "
454465,107,194,60,74,1,120,13,"Yo vā pana sakalacakkavāḷagabbhaṃ vītaccitaṅgārabharitaṃ pādehi maddamāno pāraṃ gantuṃ samattho, so buddhattaṃ pāpuṇātīti. "
454466,107,194,75,115,1,219,33,"Yo etesu ekampi attano dukkaraṃ na maññati,‘‘ ahaṃ etampi taritvā vā gantvā vā pāraṃ gamissāmī’’ ti evaṃ mahantena chandena ca ussāhena ca vāyāmena ca pariyeṭṭhiyā ca samannāgato hoti, etasseva patthanā samijjhati, na itarassa. "
454467,107,194,116,126,1,91,10,Tasmā sumedhatāpaso ime aṭṭha dhamme samodhānetvāva buddhabhāvāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipajji. 
454468,107,195,2,41,1,317,33,"Dīpaṅkaropi bhagavā āgantvā sumedhatāpasassa sīsabhāge ṭhatvā maṇisīhapañjaraṃ ugghāṭento viya pañcavaṇṇapasādasampannāni akkhīni ummīletvā kalalapiṭṭhe nipannaṃ sumedhatāpasaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ tāpaso buddhattāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipanno, samijjhissati nu kho etassa patthanā, udāhu no’’ ti anāgataṃsañāṇaṃ pesetvā upadhārento–"
454469,107,195,42,61,1,136,15,‘‘ ito kappasatasahassādhikāni cattāri asaṅkhyeyyāni atikkamitvā ayaṃ gotamo nāma buddho bhavissatī’’ ti ñatvā ṭhitakova parisamajjhe byākāsi–
454470,107,195,62,75,1,65,9,‘‘ passatha no tumhe imaṃ uggatapaṃ tāpasaṃ kalalapiṭṭhe nipannan’’ ti?
454471,107,195,76,84,1,14,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti. "
454472,107,195,85,94,1,72,8,"Ayaṃ buddhattāya abhinīhāraṃ katvā nipanno, samijjhissati imassa patthanā. "
454473,107,195,95,105,1,99,10,Ayañhi ito kappasatasahassādhikānaṃ catunnaṃ asaṅkhayeyyānaṃ matthake gotamo nāma buddho bhavissati. 
454474,107,195,106,150,1,272,35,"Tasmiṃ panassa attabhāve kapilavatthu nāma nagaraṃ nivāso bhavissati, māyā nāma devī mātā, suddhodano nāma rājā pitā, aggasāvako upatisso nāma thero, dutiyasāvako kolito nāma, buddhupaṭṭhāko ānando nāma, aggasāvikā khemā nāma therī, dutiyasāvikā uppalavaṇṇā nāma therī bhavissati. "
454475,107,195,151,167,1,196,16,Ayaṃ paripakkañāṇo mahābhinikkhamanaṃ katvā mahāpadhānaṃ padahitvā nigrodharukkhamūle pāyāsaṃ paṭiggahetvā nerañjarāya tīre paribhuñjitvā bodhimaṇḍaṃ āruyha assattharukkhamūle abhisambujjhissatīti. 
454476,107,195,168,170,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
454477,107,196,2,9,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Dīpaṅkaro lokavidū, āhutīnaṃ paṭiggaho; "
454478,107,197,2,8,1,40,5,"Ussīsake maṃ ṭhatvāna, idaṃ vacanamabravi."
454479,107,198,2,12,1,41,6,"‘ ‘‘ Passatha imaṃ tāpasaṃ, jaṭilaṃ uggatāpanaṃ; "
