454500,107,216,35,37,1,15,2,Evañcassa ahosi–
454501,107,216,38,78,1,284,32,"‘‘ yathā nāma manussā nadiṃ tarantā ujukena titthena uttarituṃ asakkontā heṭṭhātitthena uttaranti, evameva mayampi dīpaṅkaradasabalassa sāsane maggaphalaṃ alabhamānā anāgate yadā tvaṃ buddho bhavissasi, tadā tava sammukhā maggaphalaṃ sacchikātuṃ samatthā bhaveyyāmā’’ ti patthanaṃ ṭhapayiṃsu. "
454502,107,216,79,87,1,96,8,Dīpaṅkaradasabalopi bodhisattaṃ pasaṃsitvā aṭṭhapupphamuṭṭhīhi pūjetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
