454507,107,217,55,81,1,164,20,"Mayametaṃ jānāma‘ yassetāni nimittāni paññāyanti, ekantena so buddho hoti’, tvaṃ attano vīriyaṃ daḷhaṃ katvā paggaṇhā’’ ti bodhisattaṃ nānappakārāhi thutīhi abhitthaviṃsu. "
