454886,107,537,2,3,1,15,2,Koṇḍañño buddho 
454887,107,538,2,13,1,97,11,Dīpaṅkarassa pana bhagavato aparabhāge ekaṃ asaṅkhyeyyaṃ atikkamitvā koṇḍañño nāma satthā udapādi. 
454888,107,538,14,18,1,35,4,Tassāpi tayo sāvakasannipātā ahesuṃ. 
