456241,107,959,2,41,1,289,31,"31. Gocaraṃ sabbabuddhānan ti sabbesaṃ atītānāgatānaṃ buddhānaṃ gocaraṃ ārammaṇabhūtaṃ jhānaratisamappitā jhānaratiyā saṃ suṭṭhu appitā samaṅgībhūtā ahesunti attho, aññe dhammāni {desentī}ti tesu paccekabuddhesu aññe ekacce dhamme desenti, aññe ekacce iddhiyā paṭhamādijjhānakīḷāya kīḷanti ramanti. "
