456666,107,1113,11,26,1,34,5,Bodhi vuccati catūsu maggesu ñāṇaṃ( mahāni.191; cūḷani. khaggavisāṇasuttaniddesa121). 
456667,107,1113,27,35,1,84,7,Paññā paññindriyaṃ paññābalaṃ dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo vīmaṃsā vipassanā sammādiṭṭhi. 
456668,107,1113,36,69,1,137,19,"So paccekasambuddho tena paccekabodhiñāṇena‘‘ sabbe saṅkhārā aniccā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ sabbe saṅkhārā dukkhā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ sabbe dhammā anattā’’ ti bujjhi."
456669,107,1113,70,168,1,361,44,"‘‘ Avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇan’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ viññāṇapaccayā nāmarūpan’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatanan’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ saḷāyatanapaccayā phasso’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ phassapaccayā vedanā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ vedanāpaccayā taṇhā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ taṇhāpaccayā upādānan’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ upādānapaccayā bhavo’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ bhavapaccayā jātī’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’’ ti bujjhi."
456670,107,1113,169,206,1,158,17,"‘‘ Avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho’’ ti bujjhi… pe…‘‘ bhavanirodhā jātinirodho’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’’ ti bujjhi."
456671,107,1113,207,242,1,124,16,"‘‘ Idaṃ dukkhan’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminipaṭipadā’’ ti bujjhi."
456672,107,1113,243,310,1,200,32,"‘‘ Ime āsavā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’’ ti bujjhi… pe…‘‘ paṭipadā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ime dhammā abhiññeyyā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ime dhammā pahātabbā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ime dhammā sacchikātabbā’’ ti bujjhi,‘‘ ime dhammā bhāvetabbā’’ ti bujjhi. "
456673,107,1113,311,352,1,305,30,"Channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca bujjhi, pañcannaṃ upādānakkhandhānaṃ samudayañca… pe… nissaraṇañca bujjhi, catunnaṃ mahābhūtānaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca bujjhi,‘‘ yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman’’ ti bujjhi. "
456674,107,1114,2,34,1,297,29,"Atha vā yaṃ bujjhitabbaṃ anubujjhitabbaṃ paṭibujjhitabbaṃ sambujjhitabbaṃ adhigantabbaṃ phassitabbaṃ sacchikātabbaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ tena paccekabodhiñāṇena bujjhi anubujjhi paṭibujjhi sambujjhi adhigañchi phassesi sacchākāsīti, evaṃ so paccekasambuddho eko anuttaraṃ paccekasambodhiṃ abhisambuddhoti eko. "
456675,107,1115,2,28,1,127,11,"{Care}ti aṭṭha cariyāyo( cūḷani. khaggavisāṇasuttaniddesa121)– iriyāpathacariyā, āyatanacariyā, saticariyā, samādhicariyā, ñāṇacariyā, maggacariyā, patticariyā, lokatthacariyā. "
456676,107,1115,29,69,1,361,30,"Iriyāpathacariyāti catūsu iriyāpathesu, āyatanacariyāti chasu ajjhattikabāhiresu āyatanesu, saticariyāti catūsu satipaṭṭhānesu, samādhicariyāti catūsu jhānesu, ñāṇacariyāti catūsu ariyasaccesu, maggacariyāti catūsu ariyamaggesu, patticariyāti catūsu sāmaññaphalesu, lokatthacariyāti tathāgatesu arahantesu sammāsambuddhesu, padesato paccekasambuddhesu, padesato sāvakesu. "
456677,107,1116,2,42,1,356,31,"Iriyāpathacariyā ca paṇidhisampannānaṃ, āyatanacariyā ca indriyesu guttadvārānaṃ, saticariyā ca appamādavihārīnaṃ, samādhicariyā ca adhicittamanuyuttānaṃ, ñāṇacariyā ca buddhisampannānaṃ, maggacariyā ca sammāpaṭipannānaṃ, patticariyā ca adhigataphalānaṃ, lokatthacariyā ca tathāgatānaṃ arahantānaṃ sammāsambuddhānaṃ, padesato paccekasambuddhānaṃ, padesato sāvakānaṃ. "
456678,107,1116,43,46,1,18,3,Imā aṭṭha cariyāyo. 
456679,107,1117,2,38,1,266,29,"Aparāpi aṭṭha cariyāyo– adhimuccanto saddhāya carati, paggaṇhanto vīriyena carati, upaṭṭhapento satiyā carati, avikkhepaṃ karonto samādhinā carati, pajānanto paññāya carati, vijānanto viññāṇacariyāya carati, evaṃ paṭipannassa kusalā dhammā āyatananti āyatanacariyāya carati. "
456680,107,1117,39,44,1,58,5,Evaṃ paṭipanno visesamadhigacchatīti visesacariyāya carati. 
456681,107,1117,45,48,1,18,3,Imā aṭṭha cariyāyo. 
456682,107,1118,2,37,1,288,27,"Aparāpi aṭṭha cariyāyo– dassanacariyā ca sammādiṭṭhiyā, abhiniropanacariyā ca sammāsaṅkappassa, pariggahacariyā ca sammāvācāya, samuṭṭhānacariyā ca sammākammantassa, vodānacariyā ca sammāājīvassa, paggahacariyā ca sammāvāyāmassa, upaṭṭhānacariyā ca sammāsatiyā, avikkhepacariyā ca sammāsamādhissa. "
456683,107,1118,38,41,1,18,3,Imā aṭṭha cariyāyo. 
456684,107,1119,2,19,1,130,14,"{Khaggavisāṇakappo}ti yathā khaggassa nāma visāṇaṃ ekameva hoti, adutiyaṃ, evameva so paccekasambuddho takkappo tassadiso tappaṭibhāgo. "
456685,107,1119,20,51,1,239,23,"Yathā atiloṇaṃ vuccati loṇakappo, atitittakaṃ vuccati tittakappo, atimadhuraṃ vuccati madhurakappo, atiuṇhaṃ vuccati aggikappo, atisītaṃ vuccati himakappo, mahāudakakkhandho vuccati samuddakappo, mahābhiññābalappatto sāvako vuccati satthukappoti. "
456686,107,1119,52,74,1,205,21,"Evameva so paccekasambuddho khaggavisāṇakappo, khaggavisāṇasadiso khaggavisāṇapaṭibhāgo eko adutiyo muttabandhano sammā loke carati viharati iriyati vattati pāleti yapeti yāpetīti eko care khaggavisāṇakappo. "
456687,107,1119,75,77,1,23,2,Tenāhu paccekasambuddhā–
456688,107,1120,2,13,1,60,8,"‘ ‘ Sabbesu bhūtesu nidhāya daṇḍaṃ, aviheṭhayaṃ aññatarampi tesaṃ; "
456689,107,1121,2,10,1,57,7,"Na puttamiccheyya kuto sahāyaṃ, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
456690,107,1122,2,11,1,61,7,"‘ ‘ Saṃsaggajātassa bhavanti snehā, snehanvayaṃ dukkhamidaṃ pahoti; "
456691,107,1123,2,5,1,28,3,Ādīnavaṃ snehajaṃ pekkhamāno; 
456692,107,1123,6,9,1,26,3,Eko care khaggavisāṇakappo.
456693,107,1124,2,11,1,56,7,"‘ ‘ Mitte suhajje anukampamāno, hāpeti atthaṃ paṭibaddhacitto; "
456694,107,1125,2,10,1,58,7,"Etaṃ bhayaṃ santhave pekkhamāno, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
456695,107,1126,2,14,1,57,10,"‘ ‘ Vaṃso visālova yathā visatto, puttesu dāresu ca yā apekkhā; "
