456701,107,1132,2,13,1,58,9,"‘ ‘ Khiḍḍā ratī hoti sahāyamajjhe, puttesu pemaṃ vipulañca hoti; "
456702,107,1133,2,8,1,56,5,"Piyavippayogaṃ vijigucchamāno, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
456703,107,1134,2,13,1,52,7,"‘ ‘ Cātuddiso appaṭigho ca hoti, santussamāno itarītarena; "
