456708,107,1139,2,9,1,55,6,"Chetvāna vīro gihibandhanāni, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
456709,107,1140,2,12,1,61,8,"‘ ‘ Sace labhetha nipakaṃ sahāyaṃ, saddhiṃ caraṃ sādhuvihāridhīraṃ; "
456710,107,1141,2,9,1,57,6,"Abhibhuyya sabbāni parissayāni, careyya tenattamano satīmā."
456711,107,1142,2,13,1,62,9,"‘ ‘ No ce labhetha nipakaṃ sahāyaṃ, saddhiṃ caraṃ sādhuvihāridhīraṃ; "
456712,107,1143,2,11,1,58,8,"Rājāva raṭṭhaṃ vijitaṃ pahāya, eko care mātaṅgaraññeva nāgo."
