456721,107,1152,2,17,1,59,12,"‘ ‘ Ītī ca gaṇḍo ca upaddavo ca, rogo ca sallañca bhayañca metaṃ; "
456722,107,1153,2,10,1,55,7,"Etaṃ bhayaṃ kāmaguṇesu disvā, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
