456735,107,1166,2,11,1,62,7,"‘ ‘ Bahussutaṃ dhammadharaṃ bhajetha, mittaṃ uḷāraṃ paṭibhānavantaṃ; "
456736,107,1167,2,10,1,57,7,"Aññāya atthāni vineyya kaṅkhaṃ, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo."
