456771,107,1202,2,7,1,62,4,Tattha sabbesu {bhūtesū}ti khaggavisāṇapaccekabuddhāpadānasuttaṃ. 
456772,107,1202,8,10,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
456773,107,1202,11,22,1,91,7,"Sabbasuttānaṃ catubbidhā uppatti– attajjhāsayato, parajjhāsayato, aṭṭhuppattito, pucchāvasitoti. "
456774,107,1202,23,28,1,58,5,Tattha khaggavisāṇasuttassa avisesena pucchāvasito uppatti. 
456775,107,1202,29,58,1,210,24,"Visesena pana yasmā ettha kāci gāthā tena tena paccekabuddhena puṭṭhena vuttā, kāci apuṭṭhena attanā adhigatamagganayānurūpaṃ udānaṃyeva udānentena, tasmā kāyaci gāthāya pucchāvasito, kāyaci attajjhāsayato uppatti. "
456776,107,1202,59,71,1,77,11,"Tattha yā ayaṃ avisesena pucchāvasito uppatti, sā ādito pabhuti evaṃ veditabbā– "
456777,107,1203,2,7,1,41,5,Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. 
456778,107,1203,8,18,1,86,10,Atha kho āyasmato ānandassa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi–
456779,107,1203,19,42,1,138,16,"‘‘ buddhānaṃ patthanā ca abhinīhāro ca dissati, tathā sāvakānaṃ, paccekabuddhānaṃ na dissati, yaṃnūnāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā puccheyyan’’ ti? "
456780,107,1203,43,51,1,80,8,So paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā yathākkamena etamatthaṃ pucchi. 
456781,107,1203,52,56,1,44,4,Athassa bhagavā pubbayogāvacarasuttaṃ abhāsi–
456782,107,1204,2,15,1,82,10,"‘ ‘ Pañcime, ānanda, ānisaṃsā pubbayogāvacare diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacceva aññaṃ ārādheti. "
456783,107,1204,16,28,1,79,11,"No ce diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacceva aññaṃ ārādheti, atha maraṇakāle aññaṃ ārādheti. "
456784,107,1204,29,34,1,36,5,Atha devaputto samāno aññaṃ ārādheti. 
456785,107,1204,35,40,1,46,5,Atha buddhānaṃ sammukhībhāve khippābhiñño hoti. 
456786,107,1204,41,49,1,43,6,Atha pacchime kāle paccekasambuddho hotī’’ ti. 
