458192,107,1407,132,152,1,157,20,So taṃ ārammaṇaṃ gahetvā gacchanto puna kevaṭṭehi macche gahetvā sākhāsu bandhitvā pasārite jāle vātaṃ asaṅgaṃyeva gacchamānaṃ disvā tasmiṃ nimittaṃ aggahesi–
