458207,107,1409,86,112,1,249,23,"Tasmā samathena attasinehaṃ pahāya sīhova saddesu aniccadukkhādīsu asantasanto, vipassanāya mohaṃ pahāya vātova jālamhi khandhāyatanādīsu asajjamāno, samatheneva lobhaṃ lobhasampayuttadiṭṭhiñca pahāya, padumaṃva toyena sabbabhavabhogalobhena alippamāno. "
