459370,107,1841,2,10,1,71,8,Tasmiṃ antare mahānisabhatthero piṇḍāya caranto tameva vīthiṃ paṭipajji. 
459371,107,1841,11,28,1,71,11,"Upāsako disvā uṭṭhāya gantvā theraṃ vanditvā‘‘ pattaṃ, bhante, dethā’’ ti āha. "
