459608,107,1862,95,113,1,150,13,"Yantabaddhāni saṭṭhi mahātaḷākāni, kammanto dvādasayojaniko, anurādhapurappamāṇā cuddasagāmā, cuddasa hatthānīkāni, cuddasa assānīkāni, cuddasa rathānīkāni. "
