459673,107,1872,2,22,1,186,16,398. Evaṃ bhagavatā etadaggaṭṭhāne ṭhapito āyasmā mahākassapo mahāsāvakabhāvaṃ patto attano pubbakammaṃ saritvā somanassavasenaṃ pubbacaritāpadānaṃ pakāsento padumuttarassa {bhagavato}tiādimāha. 
459674,107,1872,23,40,1,180,16,Tattha {padumuttarassā}ti tassa kira bhagavato mātukucchito nikkhamanakālato paṭṭhāya pādānaṃ nikkhepanasamaye akkantakkantapāde satasahassapattā padumā pathaviṃ bhinditvā uṭṭhahiṃsu. 
