459721,107,1889,2,10,1,69,6,Sumedhaṃ bhagavantāhan tiādikaṃ āyasmato anuruddhattherassa apadānaṃ. 
459722,107,1889,11,26,1,160,15,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle vibhavasampanne kuṭumbikakule nibbatti. 
459723,107,1889,27,61,1,318,34,Vayappatto ekadivasaṃ vihāraṃ gantvā satthu santike dhammaṃ suṇanto satthārā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ dibbacakkhukānaṃ aggaṭṭhāne ṭhapentaṃ disvā sayampi taṃ dānaṃ patthetvā satasahassabhikkhuparivārassa bhagavato sattāhaṃ mahādānaṃ pavattetvā sattame divase bhagavato bhikkhusaṅghassa ca uttamāni vatthāni datvā paṇidhānaṃ akāsi. 
459724,107,1889,62,79,1,134,13,Satthāpissa anantarāyena samijjhanabhāvaṃ disvā‘‘ anāgate gotamassa sammāsambuddhassa sāsane dibbacakkhukānaṃ aggo bhavissatī’’ ti byākāsi. 
459725,107,1889,80,104,1,183,19,Sopi tattha puññāni karonto satthari parinibbute sattayojanike kanakathūpe bahukaṃsapātiyo dīparukkhehi dīpakapallikāhi ca‘‘ dibbacakkhuñāṇassa upanissayo hotū’’ ti uḷāraṃ dīpapūjaṃ akāsi. 
459726,107,1889,105,137,1,317,32,Evaṃ yāvajīvaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto kassapassa bhagavato kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ kuṭumbikagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto satthari parinibbute niṭṭhite yojanike kanakathūpe bahukaṃsapātiyo sappimaṇḍassa pūretvā majjhe ca ekekaṃ guḷapiṇḍaṃ ṭhapetvā mukhavaṭṭiyā mukhavaṭṭiṃ phusāpento cetiyaṃ parikkhipāpesi. 
459727,107,1889,138,149,1,116,11,Attanā gahitakaṃsapātiṃ sappimaṇḍassa pūretvā sahassavaṭṭiyo jālāpetvā sīse ṭhapetvā sabbarattiṃ cetiyaṃ anupariyāyi. 
459728,107,1890,2,29,1,186,22,"Evaṃ tasmimpi attabhāve yāvajīvaṃ kusalaṃ katvā devaloke nibbattitvā tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato cuto anuppanne buddhe bārāṇasiyaṃyeva duggatakule nibbatti,‘‘ annabhāro’’ tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
459729,107,1890,30,37,1,50,7,So sumanaseṭṭhissa nāma gehe kammaṃ karonto jīvati. 
459730,107,1890,38,67,1,302,29,Ekadivasaṃ so upariṭṭhaṃ nāma paccekabuddhaṃ nirodhasamāpattito vuṭṭhāya gandhamādanapabbatato ākāsenāgantvā bārāṇasīnagaradvāre otaritvā cīvaraṃ pārupitvā nagare piṇḍāya carantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso pattaṃ gahetvā attano atthāya ṭhapitaṃ bhāgabhattaṃ patte pakkhipitvā paccekabuddhassa dātukāmo ārabhi. 
