459975,107,1965,2,35,1,263,28,"515. Bhante, sakyamuni sakyavaṃsappabhava yadā yasmiṃ kāle suddhodanamahārājassa tava pitu ramme ramaṇīye kapilavatthave kapilavatthunāmake nagare tuvaṃ dhammameghena gajjati ghoseti, tadā tasmiṃ kāle ahaṃ bhārato saṃsāragabbhabhārato parimucciṃ mutto ahosinti sambandho. "
